extends partials/layout

block content
  h1.s-Title--1 Getting started
  div.Box
    div.Box-header
      h2.Box-title Structure
    div.Box-content
      ul
        li Built files are versionned into /dist folder
        li Settings and variables are set into /utils/var and can be override

  div.Box
    div.Box-header
      h2.Box-title Installation
    div.Box-content
      p Installation via GitHub and Bower are provided.
      code bower install tapestry
      code git clone git@github.com:Wisembly/tapestry.git

  div.Box
    div.Box-header
      h2.Box-title Use
    div.Box-content
      p Standalone: install Tapestry and include the following line into your website
      pre &lt;link href="__CHANGE_PATH__/dist/css/tapestry.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"&gt;
      p Sass: add the following line into your scss file
      pre @import "__CHANGE_PATH__/src/scss/app.scss";

  div.Box
    div.Box-header
      h2.Box-title Development
    div.Box-content
      p Install Node, BrowserSync and Gulp globally
      p Install dependencies: 
        code npm install
      p Start Gulp: 
        code gulp
